SUMMARY:West Ham Tech Training - SG
DESCRIPTION:INDIVIDUAL PLAYER DEVELOPMENT IN AGE GROUP SETTING<br><br>
 Improve your touch\, creativity\, and technique! ‬  Tech Training is
  individual-based player development training in an age-group setting.
  Coach Zak Matteoli\, Director of Youth Player Development\, leads the
  program.<br><br>- A technical training program for all SLSG Players.<br>-
  Sign-up is by individual player\; it is not a team event.<br>- U6 to U14
  age groups<br>- Boys and Girls<br>- Missouri and Illinois<br>- 6 sessions
  on Saturday mornings<br>- The times vary by facility (double check the
  schedule on link below) <br>- Weather-related cancellations will be
  posted on Twitter (X) - @SLSGfacilities<br>- There is no cost for SLSG
  players\, but all players need please to RSVP.<br>- There are off weeks
  in the middle of the program due to SLSG Tournaments\, double check
  schedule.<br><br>TECH TRAINING LOCATIONS:<br>Missouri - WWT Soccer Park -
  Field 6<br>Illinois - SLSG Collinsville - Turf <br><br>AGE GROUPS:<br>
 9:00am - 10:15am (U9\, U10\, U11\, U12\, U13\, U14 - boys and girls)<br>
 10:15am - 11:30am (U6\, U7\, U8 - boys and girls)<br><br>SCHEDULE:<br>
 https://bit.ly/PDT-spring26<br><br>ITEMS TO NOTE:<br>In order to staff the
  session correctly\, we ask all players to RSVP on this Playmetrics event
 <br>The cost is included in club dues. There are no make ups due to
  facility plans.<br>Weather related cancellations will be posted on
  twitter - @SLSGfacilities and if we we are able\, emailed through the
  sign-up list (we are sometimes in the field and can not).<br><br>RSVP:
  https://bit.ly/TECH-rsvp
LOCATION:1 Soccer Park Rd\, Fenton\, MO 63026\, USA
STATUS:CONFIRMED
URL:https://playmetrics.com
X-CODEX-SOURCE:playmetrics-soccer
END:VEVENT
